pageContext.course_type_long_description: Bring your engineering and creative thinking skills as we create some crazy motorized creatures! Students will be introduced to a variety of methods of movements through a series of intriguing projects. Taking inspiration from the movement of insects, sea creatures, and even our own bodies, we will have fun creating some life-like crawlers, wobblers and walkers!
